*PageRegion w288h432/4 x 6 in: "<</PageSize[288 432]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w283h425/100 x 150 mm: "<</PageSize[283 425]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w288h288/4 x 4 in: "<</PageSize[288 288]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w162h108/2.25 x 1.5 in: "<</PageSize[162 108]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*PageRegion w144h72/2 x 1 in: "<</PageSize[144 72]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
*CloseUI: *PageRegion

*DefaultImageableArea: w288h432
*ImageableArea w288h432/4 x 6 in: "0 0 288 432"
*ImageableArea w283h425/100 x 150 mm: "0 0 283 425"
*ImageableArea w288h288/4 x 4 in: "0 0 288 288"
*ImageableArea w162h108/2.25 x 1.5 in: "0 0 162 108"
*ImageableArea w144h72/2 x 1 in: "0 0 144 72"

*DefaultPaperDimension: w288h432
*PaperDimension w288h432/4 x 6 in: "288 432"
*PaperDimension w283h425/100 x 150 mm: "283 425"
*PaperDimension w288h288/4 x 4 in: "288 288"
*PaperDimension w162h108/2.25 x 1.5 in: "162 108"
*PaperDimension w144h72/2 x 1 in: "144 72"

*HWMargins: 0 0 0 0
*MaxMediaWidth: "324"
*MaxMediaHeight: "3240"
*CustomPageSize True: "pop pop pop <</PageSize[5 -2 roll]/ImagingBBox null>>setpagedevice"
