*ParamCustomPageSize Height: 2 points 36 3240
*ParamCustomPageSize WidthOffset: 3 points 0 0
*ParamCustomPageSize HeightOffset: 4 points 0 0
*ParamCustomPageSize Orientation: 5 int 0 0

*OpenUI *PrintSpeed/Print Speed: PickOne
*OrderDependency: 40 AnySetup *PrintSpeed
*DefaultPrintSpeed: 50
*PrintSpeed 10/1 in/sec (darkest): ""
*PrintSpeed 20/2 in/sec: ""
*PrintSpeed 30/3 in/sec: ""
*PrintSpeed 40/4 in/sec: ""
*PrintSpeed 50/5 in/sec: ""
